I set the locale by uncommenting the 'en_US.UTF-8 UTF-8' and the 'en_GB.UTF-8 UTF-8' lines in the /etc/locale.gen file and then ran:

locale-gen
echo LANG=en_US.UTF-8 >> /etc/locale.conf

echo laptop_name >> /etc/hostname


